'''Club Corellia''' was a [[Nightclub/Legends|nightclub]] located within the [[Core District/Legends|Core District]] of the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Cinnagar/Legends|Cinnagar]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Empress Teta/Legends|Empress Teta]]. Like many of the attractions within the Core District, the club's architecture represented a specific planet within the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]] region of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]; specifically [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. Club Corellia specialized in food, drink, [[Music/Legends|music]], entertainment, and dance from Corellia as well as a variety of other planets in the galactic core.<ref name="Wizards" />

